Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.18,0:04:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnConstantia\fs60\b1\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFAD30F&\4c&HEDE711&}さぁ光の射す方へ　僕らはいつかきっと
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.46,0:04:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnConstantia\fs60\b1\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFAD30F&\4c&HEDE711&}この繋いだ手を
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.92,0:04:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnConstantia\fs60\b1\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFAD30F&\4c&HEDE711&}君とならばずっと
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.33,0:03:23.39,Default,,0,0,995,,{\fnConstantia\fs60\b1\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFAD30F&\4c&HEDE711&}連繫著無法動搖的堅定信念
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.96,0:03:29.53,Default,,0,0,995,,{\fnConstantia\fs60\b1\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFAD30F&\4c&HEDE711&}於是今天也在尋找REASON
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.53,0:03:34.64,Default,,0,0,995,,{\fnConstantia\fs60\b1\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFAD30F&\4c&HEDE711&\pos(960,81)}Someday we'll find never faded glory
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.84,0:03:43.08,Default,,0,0,995,,{\fnConstantia\fs60\b1\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFAD30F&\4c&HEDE711&}總有一天我們定會見到從未看過的未來
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.03,0:03:54.27,Default,,0,0,995,,{\fnConstantia\fs60\b1\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFAD30F&\4c&HEDE711&}在不眠的城市中重疊的影子
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.59,0:03:58.19,Default,,0,0,995,,{\fnConstantia\fs60\b1\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFAD30F&\4c&HEDE711&}Can you hear my calling？現在也…
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.02,0:04:02.49,Default,,0,0,995,,{\fnConstantia\fs60\b1\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFAD30F&\4c&HEDE711&}在絕望的盡頭    響徹著的音樂
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.65,0:04:07.07,Default,,0,0,995,,{\fnConstantia\fs60\b1\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFAD30F&\4c&HEDE711&}不會枯萎的靈魂    沒有理由的衝動
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.07,0:04:10.46,Default,,0,0,995,,{\fnConstantia\fs60\b1\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFAD30F&\4c&HEDE711&}現在就這樣響起吧
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.03,0:04:16.40,Default,,0,0,995,,{\fnConstantia\fs60\b1\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFAD30F&\4c&HEDE711&}連繫著無法動搖的堅定信念
