Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.05,0:04:25.12,Default,,0,0,995,,{\fnConstantia\fs60\b1\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFAD30F&\4c&HEDE711&}準備開始了   未有終點的My Story
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.18,0:04:31.98,Default,,0,0,995,,{\fnConstantia\fs60\b1\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFAD30F&\4c&HEDE711&}總有一天我們定會抵達那光明的所在
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.46,0:04:36.65,Default,,0,0,995,,{\fnConstantia\fs60\b1\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFAD30F&\4c&HEDE711&}這連繫著彼此的手
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.92,0:04:43.24,Default,,0,0,995,,{\fnConstantia\fs60\b1\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFAD30F&\4c&HEDE711&}只要你我永遠一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:04:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我們去這看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.67,0:05:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,這位芥川   不是音樂科的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.32,0:05:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,芥川老師是專門研究人類文化的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,在槙原教授那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.37,0:05:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,芥川老師說現在可以見你們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.28,0:05:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.96,0:05:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,本來還以為是音樂科的老師呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,真不契合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,原來就不知情   這也沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.81,0:05:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,說的也是   謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.64,0:05:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,積極向前看就是我的信條
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.92,0:05:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,遙的這個優點   我真的覺得很佩服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,而且   這個學校   好像很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.51,0:05:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就是啊   很期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那  趕緊走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.70,0:06:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,積極向前看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.33,0:06:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\4c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fnMicrosoft YaHei UI\b1\i0\fs50\frz5.413\pos(1334.4,398.6)}我是槙原 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.33,0:06:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\4c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fnMicrosoft YaHei\b1\i0\fs50\frz3.231\pos(1216,683.4)} 關於課題可以請教芥川老師喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.76,0:06:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,打  打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.11,0:06:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有人在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.19,0:06:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害啊   有這麼多書
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.97,0:06:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,這全部都是外文書嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.22,0:06:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,看起來好深奧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,幸也同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.11,0:07:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你果然來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.44,0:07:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,幸也
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.74,0:07:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是幸也同學  對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.80,0:07:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是   是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.51,0:07:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,幸也   怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.92,0:07:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.27,0:07:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.02,0:07:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.46,0:07:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.05,0:08:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我是土佐堀遙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,擅自跟著進來這裡   真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.14,0:08:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你們兩個過來這裡坐坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.24,0:08:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.01,0:08:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.58,0:08:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微等我一下喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.50,0:08:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,可以的話   請吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不用這麼客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.57,0:08:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,從勝那裡聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.35,0:08:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,還有   我很喜歡你的音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.82,0:08:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,您的意思是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.23,0:08:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.52,0:08:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,「Y' s」是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.08,0:08:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.16,0:08:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,明明把臉遮住了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.36,0:08:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.55,0:09:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,幸也果然好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.40,0:09:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,在這裡連接上了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.67,0:09:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,到參觀的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.91,0:09:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,要不然我先離開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.52,0:09:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.41,0:09:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,時間還很充裕的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.49,0:09:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好的   我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.96,0:09:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.36,0:09:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,妳喜歡真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.31,0:09:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.02,0:09:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就先去看看了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:09:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯   抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.92,0:10:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好了   好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.84,0:10:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝招待
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.56,0:10:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你們感情真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.43,0:10:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,啊   我們從小時候就認識了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.50,0:10:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我想說的不是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.20,0:10:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,對了   您看的是哪一個視頻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.84,0:10:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,看過很多個視頻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.44,0:10:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不過你想問的是這個在「通靈塔」的問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.44,0:10:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1134.934,976.8)}Ziggurat
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.18,0:10:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,和這裡不同的別的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.56,0:10:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,您知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.93,0:10:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.04,0:10:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我曾經是 Hand Shakers
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.36,0:10:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,再多告訴我一些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.21,0:10:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,關於你的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我是不是應該和他說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.28,0:11:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.70,0:11:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,任何人都可以和你一起進入「通靈塔」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.70,0:11:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1283.734,975.2)}Ziggurat
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.36,0:11:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,只要觸碰到手的話   與任何人在任何時間都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.13,0:11:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,可是就算一起進去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.65,0:11:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,對方也無法使用「寧錄」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.65,0:11:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(1165.733,979.733)}Nimrod
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.00,0:11:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,然而從「通靈塔」出來後   對方也會失去失去記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.00,0:11:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(638.934,976.8)}Ziggurat
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.89,0:11:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,若是不加以抑制   只要碰到就會進入「通靈塔」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.89,0:11:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1426.134,976.8)}Ziggurat
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.23,0:11:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼   我會有這樣的力量呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.74,0:11:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我並不像其他的 Hand Shakers 有願望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.92,0:11:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,就連固定的搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.36,0:11:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.11,0:11:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不管什麼都不契合
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.58,0:12:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我明顯沒有抑制   為什麼沒發生意外
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.38,0:12:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,果然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經無法再進入「通靈塔」了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1166.934,976.8)}Ziggurat
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.01,0:12:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.36,0:12:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.07,0:12:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我在找人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.37,0:12:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是還在「通靈塔」裡面的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.37,0:12:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(987.734,975.2)}Ziggurat
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.62,0:12:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,在那種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.70,0:12:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是見到神的人   實現了願望的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.18,0:12:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我卻無法再見到他們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.97,0:12:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,長岡先生和檀姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.52,0:12:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,能夠尋找到他們的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.84,0:12:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,只有能自由進出「通靈塔」的你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.84,0:12:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1046.934,975.2)}Ziggurat
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.69,0:12:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.00,0:12:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,用我的力量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.14,0:13:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起   我這麼擅自的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.16,0:13:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,並沒有這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.08,0:13:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我的一些微薄之力   能有那麼一點意義的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那就請讓我幫助您吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.39,0:13:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你   幸也同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.27,0:13:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不會   那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.51,0:13:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,非常抱歉   拜託你做這麼不相關的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.51,0:13:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.42,0:13:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,從勝那裡聽說後   我就決定和你見一面了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,包括這個請求
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.73,0:13:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,還有   另外有件事   我必須向你說明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,對我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,請小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.44,0:13:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,「Y' s」的能力已經被世人所知
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.72,0:13:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你那能自由來回兩個世界的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.20,0:13:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand Shakers 的話一定會發現你的與眾不同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.18,0:14:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想助你一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.06,0:14:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,想保護你遠離傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.63,0:14:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我會去拜託大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,大家是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.99,0:14:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.95,0:14:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那些原是 Hand Shakers 的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.88,0:14:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他們有各式各樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然已經沒有「寧錄」了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(1108.133,979.733)}Nimrod
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.58,0:14:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不過肯定可以幫助你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.16,0:14:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,為了我這麼做…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.30,0:14:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,「通靈塔」的星星  果然很厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.30,0:14:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(672.534,975.2)}Ziggurat
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你就只有「厲害」一詞了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.40,0:14:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我不否定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.24,0:14:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是第一次見到如此明亮的天鵝座α星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.08,0:14:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,何況和那傢伙戰鬥真的很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.65,0:14:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但是啊   那傢伙明明那麼強
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.10,0:15:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,卻只會逃跑   正面對決才有意思嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.48,0:15:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我更中意從遠處單方面狙擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.52,0:15:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你那樣陰險的手法我完全無法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.44,0:15:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你  真的很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.04,0:15:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,這算是誇獎嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.72,0:15:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,假如能擊敗他   我們就能隨時進出「通靈塔」了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.72,0:15:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1339.734,975.2)}Ziggurat
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.88,0:15:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,要是戰勝了 Hand Shakers   就可以奪取對方的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.45,0:15:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是我倆能駕馭的    或許就可以使用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.70,0:15:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那還真是厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.16,0:15:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,永遠待在「通靈塔」  那便是我們的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.16,0:15:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(822.934,975.2)}Ziggurat
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.92,0:15:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不像這樣的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.72,0:15:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,更沒有那些無聊的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙啊   宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.14,0:15:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我想去宇宙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.25,0:15:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,說不定我們可以偷走那邊的世界的宇宙船喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.22,0:15:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,盡說些蠢話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.77,0:15:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們就去打敗「Y' s」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.00,0:15:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道他在哪嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.74,0:16:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,一處一處尋找嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.18,0:16:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你稍微等等   我們不是計劃好對策了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.54,0:16:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.08,0:16:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,說的也是   真不愧是你   好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.81,0:16:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你輕點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.08,0:16:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很強呢  「Y' s」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.52,0:16:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,如果想和「Y' s」一對一的話    那兩個男人很礙事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.29,0:16:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉啊   我只會拖後腿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.01,0:16:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,全靠小華一個人在前面戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.36,0:16:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是千里的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.20,0:16:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我真討厭 Hand Shakers
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.73,0:16:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都會襲擊我們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.68,0:16:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,真是難纏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.47,0:16:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,可是   小華卻每次都很保護我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.72,0:16:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,才沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.73,0:16:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,真想自由的牽手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.72,0:16:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,就是因為這個願望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.78,0:17:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,為了回到像以前一樣   我們必須牽手戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真是矛盾呢   但規矩的確是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.36,0:17:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,「Composer」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.40,0:17:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,讓他擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.88,0:17:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,對於和「Y' s」戰鬥這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HECFBE1&\4c&HE8FFD9&\b1\fs70\frz6.741\pos(1220.8,257.8)}妳們沒事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HECFBE1&\4c&HFFFFFF&\b1\fs70\frz6.741\pos(1384,469)}關於「Y' s」的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HECFBE1&\4c&HFFFFFF&\b1\fs70\frz6.741\pos(1414.4,563.4)}我這邊也正在分析
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HECFBE1&\4c&HFFFFFF&\b1\fs70\frz6.741\pos(1412.8,664.2)}等我的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.40,0:17:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HECFBE1&\4c&HFFFFFF&\b1\fs70\frz6.741\pos(1177.6,67.4)}妳們沒事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.40,0:17:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HECFBE1&\4c&HFFFFFF&\b1\fs70\frz6.741\pos(1363.2,299.4)}關於「Y' s」的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.40,0:17:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HECFBE1&\4c&HFFFFFF&\b1\fs70\frz6.741\pos(1390.4,390.6)}我這邊也正在分析
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.40,0:17:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HECFBE1&\4c&HFFFFFF&\b1\fs70\frz6.741\pos(1387.2,483.4)}等我的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.40,0:17:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HECFBE1&\4c&HFFFFFF&\b1\fs70\frz6.741\pos(1440,709)}這是我的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.40,0:17:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HECFBE1&\4c&HFFFFFF&\b1\fs70\frz6.741\pos(1465.6,808.2)}對於非自願成為
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.40,0:17:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HECFBE1&\4c&HFFFFFF&\b1\fs70\frz6.741\pos(1430.4,912.2)} Hand Shakers 的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.40,0:17:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HECFBE1&\4c&HFFFFFF&\b1\fs70\frz6.741\pos(1472,998.6)} 我想盡一點力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.93,0:17:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真是可疑   明明就是他們誘導我們去挑戰「Y' s」的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.16,0:17:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以這麼說   他一直以來都在給我們建議
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.25,0:17:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然真的很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.48,0:17:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,『幫助不想戰鬥的 Hand Shakers 』嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.21,0:17:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,說是只要打倒「Y' s」 能力就會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.99,0:17:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,小華是怎麼想的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.19,0:17:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,關於知道 Hand Shakers 的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.08,0:17:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,全部都是他告訴我們的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.84,0:18:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,除了第一次進入「通靈塔」時湧入腦袋的情報以外
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.84,0:18:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(872.534,976.8)}Ziggurat
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.97,0:18:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.62,0:18:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不過   還是想像之前那樣牽著手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,小華   最喜歡妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.56,0:18:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒到那個程度
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好冷淡喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.49,0:18:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但是   還是喜歡妳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.92,0:18:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不要用那麼奇怪的方式說話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.61,0:18:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,未曾謀面的「Composer」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.27,0:18:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,名字的意義是作曲家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.95,0:18:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,現在只有打倒「Y' s」這方法了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.27,0:18:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,只是   究竟要如何找到「Y' s」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.96,0:19:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,一直都是一個人嗎    幸也
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,小代理小姐真是個好人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.66,0:19:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不僅知道「Y' s」的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.32,0:19:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,還很喜歡音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.93,0:19:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,明明那麼年輕   卻已經是老師了   令人佩服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.46,0:19:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,蛋糕也很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.20,0:19:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那是她是親手做的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.81,0:19:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,從北條先生那裡聽說我們要來而專程做的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.64,0:19:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,即使有點不好意思   依然很高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.36,0:19:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我如果多練習    一定也會…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.01,0:19:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,北飛鳥學園   真是所好學校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.64,0:20:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,假設是那所學校   或許可以有些改變吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你遲遲不過來   結果還是我變成你的嚮導
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,啊   抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.62,0:20:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起啦
